_sText:
A terrorist faction has taken over an apartment building in the heart of the city. Time to take the battle to the streets! 

CTs: Rescue the 4 hostages from the apartment building.

Ts: Prevent the CTs from entering the apartment complex
and rescuing the hostages.

Notes: The hostages/terrorists start in the appartment building. There is also a parking garage for CT snipers to use (or whoever feels like it).

Map (c) 2005 |sK| [Black Dreams]

Sheik
Carst

For  the excellent prefabs.

Any questions/concerns or whatever please PM me. COMMENTS AND FEEDBACK ARE GREATLY APPRECIATED!!! 

Enjoy!

P.S. This is my first map, so let me know how I'm doing.
